1c yf2 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hest who mediates the benefits of </div><div class="t mf4 x52 h1c yf3 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lis own self-sacrifice for mankind, </div><div class="t mf5 x52 h1c yf4 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thich is lost without such ministry. </div><div class="t mf6 x1e h1c yf5 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Our personal acquaintance with </div><div class="t mf7 x52 h1c yf6 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nd relationship to our great High </div><div class="t m34 x55 h1e yf7 ff2 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nfigh [Mala </div><div class="t mf8 x56 h1c yf8 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Priest is vital to our salvation. This </div><div class="t mf9 x56 h1c ye1 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lesson, therefore, assumes that </div><div class="t mac x56 h1c ye2 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath School members possess a </div><div class="t mfa x56 h1c yf9 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">basic knowledge of the earthly </div><div class="t mfb x56 h1c ye4 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sanctuary and its services and </div><div class="t mfc x56 h1c y7d ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spends two thirds of the week in </div><div class="t mfd x56 h1c ye5 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of Him around whom all </div><div class="t mfe x56 h1c y33 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sanctuary services revolve. If ex-</div><div class="t mff x56 h1c ye7 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">planation is needed for this em-</div><div class="t m100 x56 h1c yfa ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">phasis, it is found in the week&apos;s </div><div class="t m101 x56 h1c ydc ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">memory verse, which bids us </div><div class="t m102 x56 h1c yfb ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;consider&quot; or &quot;contemplate&quot; or </div><div class="t m103 x56 h1c yfc ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;fix the mind on&quot; Christ Jesus. He </div><div class="t m104 x56 h1c yec ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is &quot;the Apostle and High Priest of </div><div class="t m105 x56 h1c yfd ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our profession&quot; or &quot;confession&quot;â€”</div><div class="t m106 x56 h1c yee ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that is, our religion. There can be </div><div class="t m107 x56 h1c yfe ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">no more Christ-centered study </div><div class="t m108 x56 h1c yff ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">than that! May its pursuit enable us </div><div class="t m109 x56 h1c y100 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to &quot;see Jesus, . . . crowned with </div><div class="t m10a x56 h1c y101 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">glory and honour&quot; (Heb. 2:9). </div><div class="t m10b x57 h1c y102 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In no sense is this only an </div><div class="t mee x56 h1c y103 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">academic study. A more spiritual </div><div class="t m10c x56 h1c y104 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(that is, related to the Spirit) and </div><div class="t m10d x56 h1c y105 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">personal topic would be hard to </div><div class="t m10e x56 h1c y106 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">choose. If we wish, it will daily re-</div><div class="t m10f x56 h1c y107 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mind us to look up and see our In-</div><div class="t m110 x56 h1c y108 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tercessor ministering on our behalf </div><div class="t m111 x56 h1c y109 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">before the Almighty, who ap-</div><div class="t m112 x56 h1c y10a ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pointed Him to that merciful work. </div><div class="t m108 x56 h1c y10b ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Those who wish to refresh their </div><div class="t m113 x56 h1c y10c ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">minds concerning this heavenly re-</div><div class="t m114 x56 h1c y10d ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ality can hardly do better than to </div><div class="t m115 x56 h1c y10e ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">make the Epistle to the Hebrews </div><div class="t m116 x56 h1c y10f ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their </div><div class="t m117 x58 h1c y110 ff5 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Further Study </div><div class="t m118 x59 h1c y110 ff2 fs11 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for this week. </div>